<div id="ripped-utopia-details" class="project-details-section">
  <h2>Ripped Utopia Details</h2>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Sign In</h3>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..1).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/ripped-utopia/slide 26/#{i}.png") %>" alt="Ripped Utopia Image" class="ripped-utopia-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Saves data locally on the phone with SwiftData, Opt-in to sign in to also save data on the cloud to prevent data loss.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="section-title">Program</h3>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Calibration of the Training Plan</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..7).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/ripped-utopia/slide 28/#{i}.png") %>" alt="Ripped Utopia Image" class="ripped-utopia-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>5 days of calibration to know your standing in the powerlifting main lifts to craft the program adapted to you, Works in both pounds and kilograms depending on your preferred unit.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Personalized Adapted Workout Program</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..6).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/ripped-utopia/slide 29/#{i}.png") %>" alt="Ripped Utopia Image" class="ripped-utopia-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Follow the plan based on a progressive overload approach to improve over time, Choose up to 4 complementary exercises to follow the compound lift.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="section-title">Exercises</h3>

  <div class="card-section">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Exercises Database</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..5).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/ripped-utopia/slide 31/#{i}.png") %>" alt="Ripped Utopia Image" class="ripped-utopia-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>The app divides exercises in a pull-push-leg split to make it easy to follow a renowned lifting rotation, Add your own exercises if your gym has different equipment or you want to customize the app exercises to your needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Deep Dive in Specific Exercises</h4>
      <div class="image-grid">
        <% (1..3).each do |i| %>
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%= asset_path("project/ripped-utopia/slide 32/#{i}.png") %>" alt="Ripped Utopia Image" class="ripped-utopia-image">
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <p>Add your lifting data based on either your All Time PR or to keep track of your Current Strength, See GIFs in a bigger format to better see how to do the movement.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="navigation-buttons">
    <a href="#exad-details" class="nav-button">← Check EXAD Project</a>
    <a href="#usf-sport-marketing-details" class="nav-button">Check USF Sport Marketing Project →</a>
  </div>
</div>
